[32m+[m[32m# Discord Moderation Bot[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mA comprehensive Discord moderation bot with advanced features for server management.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Features[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Moderation Commands**: Kick, ban, warn, timeout, and mute members[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Channel Management**: Create, delete, and configure channels[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Message Utilities**: Bulk delete messages and message management[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Role Management**: Assign, remove, and manage roles[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Utilities**: Server info, user info, ping, and more[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Setup Wizard**: Easy configuration for new servers[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Installation[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m1. Clone the repository:[m
[32m+[m[32m```bash[m
[32m+[m[32mgit clone <repository-url>[m
[32m+[m[32mcd discord-mod-bot[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m2. Install dependencies:[m
[32m+[m[32m```bash[m
[32m+[m[32mpip install -r requirements.txt[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m3. Configure the bot:[m
[32m+[m[32m   - Copy `.env.example` to `.env`[m
[32m+[m[32m   - Add your Discord bot token to `.env`[m
[32m+[m[32m   - Modify `config.yaml` to suit your needs[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m4. Run the bot:[m
[32m+[m[32m```bash[m
[32m+[m[32mpython bot.py[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Configuration[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Environment Variables (.env)[m
[32m+[m[32m- `DISCORD_TOKEN`: Your Discord bot token from the Discord Developer Portal[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### config.yaml[m
[32m+[m[32m- `bot.prefix`: Command prefix (default: !)[m
[32m+[m[32m- `moderation`: Moderation settings and auto-actions[m
[32m+[m[32m- `permissions`: Role-based permissions[m
[32m+[m[32m- `features`: Channel configurations[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Commands[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Moderation[m
[32m+[m[32m- `!kick <member> [reason]` - Kick a member[m
[32m+[m[32m- `!ban <member> [reason]` - Ban a member[m
[32m+[m[32m- `!unban <user_id>` - Unban a user[m
[32m+[m[32m- `!warn <member> [reason]` - Warn a member[m
[32m+[m[32m- `!warnings <member>` - View member warnings[m
[32m+[m[32m- `!timeout <member> <duration> [reason]` - Timeout a member[m
[32m+[m[32m- `!untimeout <member>` - Remove timeout from a member[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Messages[m
[32m+[m[32m- `!purge <amount>` - Delete multiple messages[m
[32m+[m[32m- `!clear <amount> [member]` - Clear messages from a user[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Channels[m
[32m+[m[32m- `!createchannel <name> [type]` - Create a new channel[m
[32m+[m[32m- `!deletechannel <channel>` - Delete a channel[m
[32m+[m[32m- `!lockchannel [channel]` - Lock a channel[m
[32m+[m[32m- `!unlockchannel [channel]` - Unlock a channel[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Roles[m
[32m+[m[32m- `!addrole <member> <role>` - Add a role to a member[m
[32m+[m[32m- `!removerole <member> <role>` - Remove a role from a member[m
[32m+[m[32m- `!createrole <name>` - Create a new role[m
[32m+[m[32m- `!deleterole <role>` - Delete a role[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Utilities[m
[32m+[m[32m- `!ping` - Check bot latency[m
[32m+[m[32m- `!serverinfo` - Display server information[m
[32m+[m[32m- `!userinfo [member]` - Display user information[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Setup[m
[32m+[m[32m- `!setup` - Start the setup wizard[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Permissions[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThe bot requires the following permissions:[m
[32m+[m[32m- Manage Channels[m
[32m+[m[32m- Manage Roles[m
[32m+[m[32m- Kick Members[m
[32m+[m[32m- Ban Members[m
[32m+[m[32m- Manage Messages[m
[32m+[m[32m- Moderate Members (for timeouts)[m
[32m+[m[32m- View Channels[m
[32m+[m[32m- Send Messages[m
[32m+[m[32m- Embed Links[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Database[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThe bot uses SQLite to store:[m
[32m+[m[32m- Member warnings[m
[32m+[m[32m- Moderation logs[m
[32m+[m[32m- Server configurations[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Support[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mFor issues or questions, please open an issue on GitHub.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## License[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mMIT License[m
